snippet.title: Euphoric Eugene
snippet.description:
Synthwave music/art channel.

Euphoric Eugene
http://euphoriceugene.com/

Thanks for viewing my channel, here you can find synthwave/vaporwave/retrowave/chillwave/deep trap music videos enhanced by visuals. 

To contact me for business inquiries or song submissions please send your mail to ozankmusic@gmail.com
I appreciate all submissions and try to go through as many as i can, but might not be able to reply to all.

Most of the graphics are done by me and others artists as well which are credited in the video descriptions. 

This channel works with new artists in the Synthwave genre. All songs and visuals posted on this channel are posted with permission or usage rights. 

Warning: This channel posts videos with flashing lights and visual patterns. that may potentially trigger seizures for people with photosensitive epilepsy.
